的 mini LED 显示屏的冲击力，但 Liquid Retina 面板仍然提供 500 尼特的亮度和 60Hz 的刷新率。</p><p>虽然苹果的 M2 芯片组已经推出一年了，但 15 英寸 Air 型号在 6 月份才推出，因此不太可能很快更新。如果您的重点是内容创作，MacBook Pro 可能是更好的选择。但如果您要兼顾从生产力到视频编辑的多种任务，那么 15 英寸 Air 是一个不错的选择，尤其是对于那些想要尽可能减轻重量的公路战士来说。不过，如果您想购买<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEM3NU5TTEpZP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTF1aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNDE2Mzc3ZmQtNzIzOS00ZDI0LWJhNTktMzUyY2I0ZTEyMWU5In0&amp;signature=AQAAATYmxECNPtdUpb9d1GZjgmxWNJggv7vpiy9ssVBVbiyE&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C75NSLJY" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C75NSLJY?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">256GB</a>或<a data-i13n="elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9kcC9CMEM3NkQ0UldKP3RhZz1nZGd0MGMtcC1vLTF1aC0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNDE2Mzc3ZmQtNzIzOS00ZDI0LWJhNTktMzUyY2I0ZTEyMWU5In0&amp;signature=AQAAATfrRZYNwCsaEM20GqPdUHqzTIUVGfTFHlW5V3j1R6qn&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fdp%2FB0C76D4RWJ" data-demonetize-referrer="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0C76D4RWJ?th=1" class="rapid-with-clickid">512GB</a>型号，最好尽快行动，因为库存往往很快就会售完。</p><p><em>在 Twitter 上</em><em>关注</em><a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/EngadgetDeals"><em>@EngadgetDeals</em></a>并<a data-i13n="cpos:8;pos:1" href="https://subscription